{"tid":1231332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭發聲明向公眾道歉","createTime":"2019-06-16T12:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T12:59:27.000Z","uid":67454,"like":5,"dislike":264,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"40c06b37fffc18f1bfd84555cfce88b521946962","tid":1231332,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:38:00.000Z","msg":"民陣再發起反修例遊行，政府晚上發表聲明，特首林鄭月娥向市民致歉，承諾會以最有誠意、最謙卑的態度接受批評，加以改進，為廣大市民服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你走啦我唔想搞大佢啊"},{"pid":"aa78801b8d969b1dd8e08514c62e16c02c83e04a","tid":1231332,"uid":18569,"like":50,"dislike":3,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:38:44.000Z","msg":"直播道歉啦，聲你老母"},{"pid":"0cea598c23190bb1356ad028bc9b7155353aa772","tid":1231332,"uid":29070,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"道佢老母 純文字道歉？"},{"pid":"71039ea3141a2c65f725369e07a13a34956a4b54","tid":1231332,"uid":18559,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:39:37.000Z","msg":"屌你係人就行出黎兜口兜面講"},{"pid":"1b71cbbabf6aa3f8d6bc8dd479816961f208b288","tid":1231332,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"反送中！"},{"pid":"ad2f281978ed136f88f374e789c098c76f827244","tid":1231332,"uid":186926,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"撒回呢？ 道你老母"},{"pid":"ed22a25aae5c209735014fc0040efa43ccb2bbae","tid":1231332,"uid":114186,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"道歉就撤回啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"d24e162be0946817854e754356f983a41ce96f49","tid":1231332,"uid":438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"我要跨張過野野村，唔係唔收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1352dced1efa9489fae333dd8f5708a3c0a39842","tid":1231332,"uid":33170,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"道歉有乜撚用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撤回惡法啦"},{"pid":"0a324d8ede9fed9a4ba7890e395a8793456bc644","tid":1231332,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/16/P2019061600738.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201906%2F16%2FP2019061600738.htm&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=d92f699d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/16/P2019061600738.htm</a><br />\n政府回應遊行<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  就今日（六月十六日）的遊行，政府發言人作出以下回應：<br />\n <br />\n  過去兩個星期日，十分多市民透過遊行表達意見，政府明白市民遊行是出於對香港的關心和熱愛。<br />\n   <br />\n  對於市民一直以平和、理性方式表達意見，行政長官清楚聽到，並認同這正是香港作為一個文明、自由、開放、多元的社會，一直展現的互相尊重、和而不同的精神。政府重視和珍惜香港這些核心價值。<br />\n   <br />\n  考慮到社會有強烈不同的意見，政府已停止立法會大會對修訂《逃犯條例》的工作，希望藉此可讓社會盡快回復平靜和避免任何人受到傷害。政府重申並無重啟程序的時間表。<br />\n   <br />\n  行政長官承認由於政府工作上的不足，令香港社會出現很大的矛盾和紛爭，令很多市民感到失望和痛心，行政長官為此向市民致歉，並承諾會以最有誠意、最謙卑的態度接受批評，加以改進，為廣大市民服務。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年6月16日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間20時29分"},{"pid":"d4772752b6d25dadd4eb65783ad67ed1dce30faa","tid":1231332,"uid":36321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"道你老母"},{"pid":"5ee742fff1a68829914cfd82ae2d8c76f2722c94","tid":1231332,"uid":15211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:41:13.000Z","msg":"唔夠膽行出嚟面對市民？！"},{"pid":"0b99348bf6d98f867a401ed6f0d7bca7d8b9e536","tid":1231332,"uid":251925,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"唔撚洗你服務<br />\n躝啦垃圾"},{"pid":"0cb530abf5c61b1021410a286d36163fdb1f35d9","tid":1231332,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"佢算唔算撤回左，佢話政府已經停止逃犯修例"},{"pid":"4c72e6ec800a3ccb4b0f98eea58176239e3a224d","tid":1231332,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:41:25.000Z","msg":"露出胸部？"},{"pid":"e9d427f8b1d47ada068636377b059627e20